{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Echoes of Karma is a game about a flirty demon and gay magician who travel the multiverse. As they travel, they discover a threat known as Glitch. The game is a turn based RPG, but with Blocking Mechanics during the enemy turn. Save TP by skipping your turn to use higher level abilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features Include|</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Episode Based Storytelling inspired by cartoons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Built in No-Hit mode (put on the tied HP mode and 1HP mode for the ultimate challenge!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-6 episodes with 6 more in development</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Simple but dynamic turn based mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-1 &quot;Ultra Boss&quot;, bosses that challenge your gameplay abilities to the fullest (3 total in the whole game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Customizable Boss Rush </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-And More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Planned Features|</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Art Museum: Look at character sheets and additional artwork after completing an episode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Theater Mode: Watch cutscenes without the need to battle enemies or bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Jukebox Mode: Listen to the game's ost, unlocked by completing episodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Note: Game is best played with a controller.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">F4 to toggle full screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Send all bug reports to <a href=\"mailto:eokbugs@gmail.com\">eokbugs@gmail.com</a></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727133715","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2523640/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727133715","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea